Usage: reportCapViolation [-help] [-excNetFile <fileName>] [-max] [-min]
                          [-outfile <fileName>] [-selNetFile <fileName>]
                          [-significant_digits <integer>] [-useDrcMargin] [-all  | -noGlobalNets ]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
-all                              # Report all option  (bool, optional)
-excNetFile <fileName>            # List of Nets not to optimize 
                                  # (string, optional)
-max                              # Max constraint option  (bool, optional)
-min                              # Min constraint option  (bool, optional)
-noGlobalNets                     # NO global net option  (bool, optional)
-outfile <fileName>               # Output file name  (string, optional)
-selNetFile <fileName>            # List of nets to optimize 
                                  # (string, optional)
-significant_digits <integer>     # Number of significant digits option 
                                  # (int, optional)
-useDrcMargin                     # Use DRC margin option  (bool, optional)